fields.name: Description
fields.description: Detailed description of the APIs available on the Gateway instance (default: `Generated OpenAPI 3 document that describes the API routes configured.`)

fields.name: Documentation
fields.description: Location of additional documentation for the APIs available on the Gateway instance

fields.name: ServerUrl
fields.description: Base URL that API consumers will use to access APIs on the Gateway instance.

fields.name: Title
fields.description: Title describing the context of the APIs available on the Gateway instance (default: `Spring Cloud Gateway for K8S`)

fields.name: Version
fields.description: Version of APIs available on this Gateway instance (default: `unspecified`).
